{
  "texts": [
    "Nodules that are 3 mm or larger and accepted by at least three of four radiologists are included in the reference standard.",
    "Thus, nodules smaller than 3 mm or annotated by only one or two radiologists are excluded.",
    "Finally, 888 low-dose CT images are generated.",
    "The LUNA16 dataset did not initially include malignancy labels.",
    "For our preparation, we updated it with the radiologists' malignancy markings corresponding to patient IDs from the metadata CSV file provided with the LIDC-IDRI dataset."
  ]
}